  "Description": {
    "English": "This complex mechanical unit was once the central combustion chamber at the heart of a <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinel Hardframe</span> unit.<br><br>Though now cool to the touch, it still glows with a sinister red heat...",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "构造极其复杂的机械单元，曾经是一台<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫强化外壳</span>单元中央燃烧室的心脏。<br><br>尽管现在摸上去十分冰冷，但其中仍然闪烁着不详的炽热......",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這個複雜的機械單元曾經是<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警硬體結構</span>單元核心中的中央壓縮艙。<br><br>雖然現在冷卻到可以觸碰，仍然散發著險惡的紅熱......"
  },
